\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Now I shall have to think. What do yo
u mean, bedrooms and downstairs? Well, three bedrooms across the top, in the front. One, two - three at the back. That was upstairs. No attics. Downstairs, two big front rooms and a hall in the front. And two - like kitchens - out at the back. And - big g
arden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Any out houses or anything like that?
