\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember anything about the house at Combe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did anybody else besides your parents and brothers and sisters live in the house with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your mother pay anybody to help in the house during the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 My mother did you say? Yes, we had - well in those days you called them servants didn't you, they wouldn't have - like that today. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did she live in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How many servants were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Only one. At a time. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where did she sleep?
