\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did she have anywhere in the house where she would sit when she wasn't working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - there was a nice kitchen, that she was in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your mother sort of supervise the work in the house that she did or did the girl get on with it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well she got on a lot of it and my - I mean my mother helped, it wasn't that she was just idle. She - she helped with it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you feel at ease with the girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
