\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh I was just - Dorothy and - Bob was me brother. Oh I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What would she have called your mother? Or your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I think, if I remember rightly, she just said Mrs Dunkley. I don't remember anything else. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your mother sort of as it were give any moral guidance to her at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I should think so because both my - father and mother were - very keen }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 
\endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141  chapel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
goers in those days, which of course would lead to that wouldn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were they allowed any time off to do what they liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
