\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So she went to meetings in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you think your mother would have minded what she did when she went out if she at chapel?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I should think so, but - very reasonable, but - especially in those days you know you had to ve very careful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was there anybody specially responsible for looking after the children? Was the girl expected to look after you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well yes, she would do, if - my mother and father went to a meeting and - you know, - she didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did the housework go, who did the housework?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Chiefly - the girl, but - as I said, you know, my mother was always helping. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That would be cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was the washing done in the house or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 By the girl again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who made or mended the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 My mother chiefly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who did the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 My mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 The girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, she would if - necessary she would do it but - generally my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who was responsible for as it were repairs and things to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh it was - it was the Duke of Marlborough's house you see so he was responsible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So your father wouldn't do painting or anything like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No, very - very little if any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you as a child have any special jobs you had to do at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Small jobs. Dusting, that kind of thing, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember any others specially?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, we - we didn't have a lot to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your brother have similar little jobs to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Yes, just little jobs, I remember in those days he used to clean the knives, he didn't like that. Of course you don't clean knives today do you. Those days we had to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How long did you go on doing these sort of jobs, after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Let me think back. Yes, I did. Odd - odd jobs you know. 'Course when we came to - Woodstock to live, we all had to buckle in because it was a different life altogether you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That was after 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 After your mother was a widow?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you help your brother with things he found difficult to do? Doing up his boot laces, that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, yes, I expect as - like a sister would, I don't remember much about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What time did you have to go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Between eight and nine, accord - when you got a bit older. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who put you to bed, your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, well we - she would but - we - we had to go ourselves and then she'd always come and see us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How old were you when you started going yourself?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What would I be? Oh I should - I should think it was when we were around nine. We used to go up on our - up on our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you share a bedroom with your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the arrangements for sleeping, the girl had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
One room. My brother had one, and I did. And - mother and father would, which left always - the bathroom, we'd got a bathroom even in those days which - wasn't always, and - they had the big room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where was the bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Out at the back. More - the back of the - house, upstairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have running water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Running hot water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I don't think there was hot, we used - I - I - 'cos I could remember - helping to carry hot water up, we'd got t
he other you see but - wasn't any way of - of heating much in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How often did you bath, was there a special bath}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, we always had a great ceremony bath}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 nights. When we - either Friday or Saturday night. Fires lit and oh yes, ever so different than it is today. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You had those clean clothes on then as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the girl help bath you or did your mother do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where did you eat your meals, did all the family eat their meals together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Bar - yes, the whole - the family, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where did the girl eat?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Same time but - in the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And where did you eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well there was a dining and a front room in the house you see, we were always in the dining room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of cooking equipment did you have in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 A stove, coal stove.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Like a range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What time in the morning would you have had breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Between - generally between eight and half past, because
 my father had to go - to work start the men at work and then he used to come home to his breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did he have anything before he went out to start the men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - he could have done but - we were never up. I can't remember that one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So your father came back at eight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of food did you eat at breakfast, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What - oh - usual eggs and bacon and - sausages and - always finished up with bread and butter and marmalade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have special breakfasts on any days, such as Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, not special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about lunch or dinner, when was that eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 About half past twelve to one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And everybody would be there, your father as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of food would you have for that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - the usual Sunday joint and - stews and - more or less what we eat today I think really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was Sunday dinner a sort of big thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, you - you - did really have the joint then you see. And in those days we - we had a joint.
 Today you can't dare ask for one now can you. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about evening meals, how did those work out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Tea and supper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When did you have tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, just an ordinary bread and butter and jam and cakes, you know, that - usual tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That would be about four?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I think he generally came in about five - for tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So you waited 'til your father had finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So everybody would have their meal together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That's true.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Supper was - well - myself and brother of course had our - small supper in those days and my mother and father when we'd gone to bed.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you and your brother have your supper in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Sometimes. Not always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 The girl would eat you say at the same time as you for all meals and in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who would do the serving then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - the girl - sometimes would bring it in, or my mother would fetch, you know, it it was - arranged between them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your mother or the girl make anything like bread, did your mother make her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Sometimes, but not as a general rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Pounds and pounds of jam. We'd got a huge garden, we'd got fourteen damson jars - dam - damson trees I mean, and she did 
really make a huge lot of jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about bottling fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Plums from your garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, all from the garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Nothing from anywhere else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - unless we went blackberrying - you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - chiefly onions I can remember, and walnuts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about wine or beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Or medicines or any sort?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And your mother made these mostly did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Made what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 The jam?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Well, between 'em. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you grow any vegetables in your garden as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, everything. Everything you could think of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So you had plum trees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Apple trees and - currant trees and - you know, everything really - was a - such a big place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So you didn't buy much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not in that way, no. Oh - no, not much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you buy tinned fruit, do you remember any tinned fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I can remember having some but - really in those days you know people - liked their own fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was tinned fruit considered very special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh I don't think so, 'cos we didn't have a lot. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who did the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well chiefly my father. But - sometimes he used to have a - a man from the estate you see - they'd - let them come out and do some of it.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 As it were the Duke would pay the man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. OH no, no, he never - he didn't have anybody in then. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you keep any hens or pigs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, hens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, and ducks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How many did you keep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - oh what shall I say, about ten - hens I should think and three or four ducks, not a lot.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So did your father look after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What did he do with the eggs and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Ate them mostly. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the chickens, were they killed eventually and eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. But - that was a hard job because we all looked on them as pets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the ducks, the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, same thing. And we had one or two pigs at one time. But that was such a difficult job to - kill them, it was packed up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your father buy the pigs in Woodstock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, can't remember - I shouldn't think - I should think he'd - would have them off a farmer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You ate meat most days did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the children and servants and adults have the same food or did they have different food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And the servants ate separately?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Ate in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But at roughly the same time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, but - within reason. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Could you choose to have what you liked from off the plates on the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 More or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But some you would be expected to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 To eat the - the main - the main ones. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What if you left stuff on your plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well we - I mean you weren't absolutely made to sit there and eat it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 If there was something you couldn't reach on the table could you ask for it to be passed to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about bringing books or toys to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. Not to the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about leaving the table at the end of a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Trying to think. We were - made to sit five - minutes - after we'd eaten. And then we could go even if the others hadn't finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Why were you made to sit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Really they thought it was good for you - not to rush round you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you always have the same places at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember how they were, where would your father sit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, it was a big oval table. We generally - he was at the head and - we were - round it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who served the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 My father - with the joint, and my mother generally the other.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 About your mother again, was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So if you had any worries or anything like that you could go to her with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did she show affection towards you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. But not - not overpowering.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about your father? Was he an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not so easy as my - mother I don't think. But you could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But you probably wouldn't have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, you'd go to - my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you know if your brother found the same thing there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I should think - it would be about the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was he affectionate towards you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, but - as I said, not - not over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the girl who came and looked after you, would you find her easy to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But you would take your problems to your mother rather than to talk to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Even when you were quite small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was she affectionate towards you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What, the girl? Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 She'd pick you up and cuddle you and that sort of thing?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you know how your parents expected you to behave towards them? Do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 We - you had to behave - reasonably well, yes, else we were - punished, never smacked. They didn't believe in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about towards your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 The same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about towards the girl who came? How they expected you to behave towards her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh we - we had to be - decent, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did the girl who came expected you to behave towards her, did she -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh she was - well she wasn't a terrific lot older than us when she came, you see, so - I don't quite know how to answer that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did she see you as a younger sister almost?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well almost, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 If you - did the girl ever tell you how to behave towards your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, she would if we were - naughty. I expect we were at times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
If you were hit by another child, or brother did, what would your parents say, would they say you should go and hit him back or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I don't remember it - ever happening, but - they
 would have wanted in those days to find out the why and the wherefore, and who was to blame. But it - never arose that I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You say your mother and father were chapel, do you think that might have had something to do with how they would answer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. It - it could do, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What kind of person do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be, you and your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well probably better than we have done. Don't you think, I - I think all parents do. But - I don't think they 
were very - not worried with us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What do you think they consider important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well, behaviour was one, and - manners to other people and etcetera. And - of course these - chapel meetings, there were a lot of that in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about work? Did they ever say anything about hard work? Did they consider that important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 To work, yes. But - not strict to say hard work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you think the girl ever say anything about what she thought was important that was any different from your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What do you think your parents would have thought about swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh no swearing. No. I've never heard my father swear, never in his - as long as - I can remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did he disapprove of it in people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. In - real - life, he didn't agree with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What - when grown ups were talking, when you parents were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Sometimes. Yes. But we were very often told it was - they had to be seen - and not heard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 If you did something wrong, what your parents thought was wrong and they disapproved of, were you punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Yes - you went to bed for an hour or - or you - had something you really - liked, that was stopped or - playtime was - stopped. That kind of thing you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who as it were decided that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I think between them. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not specially your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How often do you think this happened?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not - not - very often. No, I don't remember - a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember any special time it happened and why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Mm - I really can't remember a special one, I can remember - I was always so fond of cats and I had a cat - well a kitten that would scratch such a lot. And while I was out - my father took it to a farm. And I went
 and fetched it back. So I wasn't very popular then, I - I had a punish then, I - I think it was a matter of - probably saw where I wanted to go - and when they said anything in those days - you didn't go. You had your punishment you see, today there's so
 much of - saying no - and they allow them to do it isn't it. But not - not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember how you felt about being punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well didn't like it. No, I mean, we knew - that we'd done wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Can - do you think you received your ideas on what was important in life from one or from both of your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Both. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You wouldn't say one was more important than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the girl who came, did you think that she had any influence on you in this way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 She might have done, yes. But - but it was chiefly me - father and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you feel about the girl who came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Always liked her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It was the same one for most of the time was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Most of the time. Well that I can remember you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was your birthday a very special day, an extra special day for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Always. Picnic. Always if - yes, and in those days you know we used to have some glorious summers. And it was always a picnic.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Could you tell me what would happen on a birthday when you were about nine or ten?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, always this - picnic was the big thing you know having all my friends and - invited.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where would you have it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It was on a hill called Leys Hill - in Hanborough. Do you know Hanborough at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Church Hanborough is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
No, this is Long Hanborough. Do you know - I don't know whether it's still there - a very big tree - up by - Swan - Swan Hill, that is the hill, right through the village and it goes 
down to Combe. You know - that's there. Well - right on the top - was a very big tree, do you remember it? Yes, well - where we lived was just opposite that you see. And then we used to go down to Swan Hill - and across some fields, and it was by the rive
r and we could paddle, and that was a - a big day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you go, just walk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, it wasn't very far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You'd invite your friends would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How many would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh perhaps ten or twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And your mother and ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And - probably - the girl you see would come to help.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Would your father come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, if he'd finished work in time he'd - join us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And you'd all take a picnic of what sort of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh diff - much about, you know, bread and butter and jam and - fruit and - that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you play games there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you get presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Can you remember about Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh, big day. We generally came to - Woodstock. For Christmas Day, to my mother's parents you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When would you get your presents, the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Now when did - after breakfast. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So you'd have breakfast at Hanborough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, breakfast we used to come and stay here, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Whereabouts was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Do you know any - where In Woodstock much? Well - go across here, down - Burns Lane, you know, and there's a big house called White House, on the left. Well that's where my parents - my grandparents lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That was the ironmongers, Brotherton's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How long would you stay there at Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Matter of few days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 The big day would be Christmas lunch time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who would be at Christmas lunch, do you remember the sort of people who would be there, would it be all family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well - who - whoever cold be, there was - two brothers and two sisters with my mother, but - whoever could be of those four were - at it you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And your grandparents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
