\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh we - we've been to Eastbourne and places, you know, generally to the seaside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How long did you go for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 A fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of place would you stay in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - what you'd call I suppose a hotel today.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the girl go with you for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You'd have bed and breakfast or full board?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, full board as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So you went away for two weeks, you went away most years that you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who went, did everybody go in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 The four you see, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of things did you do when you were on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, the same thing on the sands that children do today you know and - different little outings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 The girl didn't come with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did she go home to her parents then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, she'd have her holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Could you tell me how you spent Saturday in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Mostly playing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was it a day on which you got ready for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Everything that you could do - was done. So that you had a really - easy Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How were Sundays spent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Sunday school and chapel in the morning. Sunday school in the afternoon. And chapel in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have different clothes for Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. All - always - a best rig-out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And you had to wear it all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you play games on a Sunday at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, but not - racing about and - you know, playing out in the streets, we weren't allowed to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So your parents obviously thought to some extent it was wrong to play games on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What were you allowed to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh well, I mean you could read at home or you could have little game of ludo or - you know, amongst ourselves, that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have Sunday books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I can't remember, no, I can't remember. I can remember the books but I don't know what they were called.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were they religious books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Probably - a religious trend. But interesting to children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Your parents did go to chapel, what sort of chapel was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What - Wesleyan. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In Hanborough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In Hanborough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How many times a day did they go on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - we all had to go the four times. You see, because they were teachers - in the Sunday school.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You talked a bit about - can you tell me a bit more about Sunday school outings? There was one a year was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, just one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, during the summer, you see. And pick a good 
day and - and some farmer would - oblige with the wagon, horses, and you'd probably go out to - a farmer. And - was a picnic provided you see and all games - for the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I was going to say ring o'ring 
a roses, but we were a bit older than that you know, I can't remember. But all together. Games all - together, but I just can't remember - what they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And you went in a wagon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Provided by a farmer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you take part in any other social activities in the church or chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well there were different - different meetings to go for children. We - in those days it was - one was called Band of Hope. And we used to go to that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That was in your chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That was in the chapel, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That was a temperance organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did that have an outing or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I - I don't think so, well no I think we used to have - what they used to call in those days - a social. Wher
e you - went into the schoolroom - and - you had games and a meal, and - singing and all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That's the Band of Hope?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When would that be, what time of the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well that was generally more - dark nights because I can remember - going in the dark to those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You had a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Games and a meal. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes. The children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 s choir really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did that have any sort of social activities with it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Don't remember those, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was grace said in your family at mealtimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well it was at my grandparents. I think it was at home, but I'm a little bit vague on that but I - I think it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did father say it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. If - if anybody he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. I don't remember those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your father take any interest in politics at all do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - not to be really - active.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 A Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Have you got any idea why he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No I haven't, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about your mother?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 She was the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember your father and mother voting in any elections before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I've got - faint recollections - of him - going to some election, because they wo
re - big - rosettes you know in those days, according to whatever the colour was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That's very interesting because of course the Duke of Marlborough was a Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you know if there was any trouble ever about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Never a
ny trouble because - on the car it had to be - the Dukes colours you see. Because it was the Duke's car, but - it was never any difficulty. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And your father drove the Duke's car?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 With the Duke's colours, wearing a rosette?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. But - when he'd finished - work you see, he could wear his own. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember your father ever saying that anybody round here was a Liberal working man say had got into trouble with his employers?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, I've never heard him say it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was he actually a member of the Liberal party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - that - that's a bit vague in my memory, I don't really remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Reading and - friends coming in and - used to have - they were very fond of a game of - whist, you know, with their friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did they go to chapel meetings in the week at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Sometimes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your mother have any interests outside the home do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not other than going to meetings - with my father.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 At the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did she ever go out on her own to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Yes, they - they used to go out amongst their friends and that kind of thing, oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But if your mother went out who would she go out with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well this one that I'm talking - I'm talking about that's lived - right through 'til now, they were very good - friends you see, and some go - go to Oxford, and that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of things would they go to Oxford for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Shopping or - probably there might be a big - chapel meeting. There you see they'd got to - that or different meetings like that. In those days I think there were a lot more meetings that people were really interested in. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What did your father do when he got home from work in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What time would your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Generally about five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What would he do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Gardening - in the summer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well mostly - all - unless they were out together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did he go to any club or to a pub at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 He - he was a Freemason. I remember that, he used to - go to those meetings you see. Oh not - did you say a club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 A club or a pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, no pub. Deadly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 He was a temperance man was he?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Terribly. Yes, very much so. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was he actually active in the temperance cause, did he speak at meetings or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well at small meetings, he wouldn't go out - to - big meetings, but - in the chapel way of - meetings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In the villages around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, I don't remember that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 He was a freemason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where did they meet, did they have a hall in Woodstock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I think they used 
to come to Woodstock. Yes, in fact - yes, they did, 'cos the Freemason hall - now - if it's - I think it still works, it's out in New Road, if you know that. It's - it's up towards the school. Mm. And - yes, he used to come to - Woodstock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your mother go to the temperance meetings and things with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So she was temperance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, both, they were very much that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your father take part in any sport at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 He liked tennis, but not to go out to play, only amongst his friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where would he play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well we had got a tennis court, so he used to invite - his friends there, and he used to go out to the different farms, the - to play tennis.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did he ever go to horse racing at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I don't remember that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 He belonged to the freemasons, did he belong to any savings club or anything like that at all do you remember?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I don't remember that, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you get on well with your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When you went to play as a child who did you play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well we'd got friends in the different houses you see, and we either went to their house or - they came to our - ours and - we had big skipping goes in those days out in the street, and of course you were perfectly
 safe you see. Was only horses and carts. And - a whole lot of you would - join for that, and hopscotch - the old game of hopscotch. That - we had a lovely childhood. Beautiful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What other games did you play in the street, can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well
 there would be hide and seek, 'cos we'd got this huge garden you see, there was plenty of room. And - yes, we had - we had - we had a good - we had a good time in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your brother play as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. We'd all play together, not always but - but he would do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 He was two years younger than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Five. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How old was he when he started playing just with boys? Or did he always play in with the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, he - he got to - well he wasn't very old you see when we left H
anborough. And - you see, then he went to school when he left - there, being a Freemason - they've got a big school haven't they somewhere, I don't remember where, where a lot of these - children - and my brother was one of them, see they had free schooli
ng. I don't remember much about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where did you play mostly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In the garden. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But you also played in the street?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, because - there was nothing to worry about in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you play in other peoples homes at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have a room in the house which was where you could play if it was raining say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well not necessary, we'd a big garage, we could go into if it was - pouring, and we'd got a - what you'd call a - we - in those days called a su
mmer house. Which - round by the - tennis lawn, we could go in there you see in the summer. But otherwise - indoors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Yes. You weren't too strict on that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were you free to play with anybody you pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Within reason. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What do you think was the reason bit there? Who do you think they'd have not been very happy if you'd played with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well in - those days - it's not so much today, but in those days - there were reall
y what you call dirty families, they were really brought up dirty, well - we were barred from that. But otherwise pretty free and easy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of people would the dirty families be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - the really poor. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Just the Band of Hope?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. And the - Sunday school, yes. YES.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have any hobbies when you were at school as a child, I mean collecting things or keep pets or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I was - was very fond of pets, yes, but weren't allowed a lot, cats and rabbits and - that - type of thing you see. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you do gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. A little bit. We had little bits to - belonged to we.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were you at all interested in sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I liked tennis, but I - you - I've never been - mad on sports, but - I did like tennis.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you go to any theatres at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 The odd one, if something was - good in Oxford they'd take us there and the same to the pictures.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, there were - in the village hall very often a college - a concert got up you see, we could go to that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about - that was just in the village did you come anywhere else for concerts or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you go to Oxford for concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - it would generally be the theatre.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about music halls, was there one at all that you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Don't remember. No, I don't think there was one about here. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Pocket money. No, I don't think so, if we wanted money you'd - you'd got to ask. And you got if if it was reasonable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What did you spend your money on when you got it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Sweets. Well there was never anything else really we wanted. It was all got for us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where did you buy your sweets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In a - village. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Part from the girl that came in, did anybody else help your mother look after the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well sometimes at - spring cleaning was a big time in those days, everything had to be cleaned, top to bottom. And - get help in then.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where would that be from, would they hire somebody extra?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Little extra woman would come in you see and help with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about friends or neighbours, would they help at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not as a rule. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So it was only just spring cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who would the person be who'd come and do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - probably - a farm labourer's - wife or something like that you see would come in in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Again from the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did a lot of people do that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well we managed with this - girl. And my father was very good, he could cook and all that kind of thing you know, if necessary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember what happened when your brother was born? You'd be very young then of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, well only about five. And he was - I think I came over to - my grandparents. In fact I - I can remember, yes, I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You had your grandparents living in Woodstock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How often did you see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Probably once a week - you know - we did come fair amount.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have any other relatives living round here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Plenty of aunts and uncles and cousins all round the town. But we didn't really - go to them like we did to the grandparents.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So that you would see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You would see them at Christmas you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Would you see them at any other times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes - about the town, but we didn't visit a lot. Occasionally but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your parents have friends in Hanborough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Where did they see them? When did they see them and where?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well at tennis - 'cos they both liked tennis. And they used to get up these little tennis parties you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did they share the same friends pretty much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your mother have any friends of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well this particular one I'm telling you about was the special one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How would she see her, would she go to her house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, and - she'd come to - my mother. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about your father, did he have friends of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well there again I should think so because they'd chiefly be out on these farms, he was always travel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 ing from - one farm to another you see, and that was chiefly where he used to - get his friends.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the friends of your parents ever come to the home? To your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How often would they come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - just casual. Yes, they'd come, yes, and - like - wise - we'd go there casually, not always - invitation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were invitations the rule usually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In those days yes, it was all - come to our place for tea today and - then it was - back again you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 If somebody came by casually would they be offered something to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes. Always - offered tea you see, always - a meal. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was there particular days or occasions that people came to visit you or that your parents went visiting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, if you were in and people - came, well then they just came in and stayed to tea as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were the people who were invited in your father's friends or your mother's friends or both?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, chiefly they were - both, I mean they - it was chiefly that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did friends call in casually then without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes. Yes, I can remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about neighbours, would they call in the same way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, there were several in the - village that would - well in those days we used to call it pop i
n, oh we'll pop in and see so and so, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So that was quite all right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 People often say that in those days people had to make their own amusements.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, yes, you did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of things do you think that your parents would do when they got together with their friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well there was always a game of cards, whist, if - they wanted to. Or - sing-song. Then in the summer of course it was generally - oh, another game, croquet, we had a croquet lawn, well it was eit
her - those who couldn't play tennis - played croquet. And - that's how they - used to do it you know. They were never - what should I - say - never without something to do, if you had a quiet - evening, well - they'd got a - a gram}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 phone, in those days you know, and it was an old fashioned - cylinder t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 y}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 pe. I don't know - have you ever seen them? Yes. Oh we got - no end of those. Well they'd have that on you see, and of course that was - something in those days. Wasn't it? Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Many people think that certainly before 1914 there was a very rigidly divided class society, divided up into different groups.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you think in the village where you lived, in Hanborough, did you think of it as being divided like this very definitely?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, I - I think we did. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Could you tell me what you think the different ones were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well - you - there was the - the so called - upper - round here, then there was the middle which we - always termed ourselves, and then there was the real - not I suppose really - really poor, because there was some in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of people belonged to the same middle group as you would you say in Hanborough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - there were - we'd got some friends in shop - keepers - there was a baker. We wer
e all very friendly with in the - and - and the farmers - round, was two or three farms in - Hanborough - we were all - all more or less friendly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of people do you think belonged to the upper group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 There wasn't a lot in Hanborough. Trying to think. I don't think here was a - really a lot - that you'd term above a farmer. NO.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the clergy, the Church of England clergyman?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What group would he be in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh he - he - you would look - up to him a bit. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But your chapel minister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh he was - one with you. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the very lowest group of all? What sort of jobs would people do who lived in that sort of group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, chiefly as - I said, farm labourers because - there was a lot o
f farms in those days. And of course they didn't get - very much money in those days. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Can you remember being brought up to treat as it were one sort of people differently or deferentially at all from another? Being told to curtsey or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not even to the Duke?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Can't ever remember - meeting him, you see, I wasn't very old. Even in those - I - I don't even think if I - had have done, I should have to behave myself but - no, I don't think any of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was there anybody you would have called sir or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember anybody in the village calling your mother or father sir or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - some of the men might have called my father that. But - not - not in the village. That would be in his work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
The man who came help do your father's garden, would he call your mother - he'd probably call your father sir because he worked for him, what would he call your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Just her - name I think, I don't remember anything other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Who were considered the most important people in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well - the Rector. And - oh no, I don't think we'd got a doctor. I don't think so But it would be that - type of person. I don't think there was one. At our time.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And of course the Duke?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - yes, but - you know, he wasn't in the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about shopkeepers, who would they associate with do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What, the shopkeeper, well - more or less we were the - clan like really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the village teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, I should think - all in together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about the farmers, were the farmers in that group as well, all the farmer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well they were all friends of ours, whether that was due to work - I - I - I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of people would you say went to church, rather than chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well really much about the same kind, it's just a matter of - religion I think. Because the church was always a bit higher than the - chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What do you mean higher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In - the service was - I don't know how you put it - oh - well higher - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It's higher in the sense of having gowns and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, that kind of thing. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were there many farm labourers in your chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh I can't remember who would be a farm labourer. It's a long time ago. No, I - really can't remember that one, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
You said that you had a number of girl servants living in, one after another, could you tell me how many there were and how long they stayed for roughly, each one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, I can't tell you - the amount of time. As far as I remember, when we lived at Hanborough there was only two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But one of them?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, the - the one I was talking about, she was the the - longest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 She was there for quite a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, quite a - well, a few years - I remember, but I don't remember the real time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 She came there from school did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. It was her first job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember anything about - you said the girl lived in one of the rooms upstairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Can you remember what sort of room it was, what it was like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh a nice bedroom, nice size, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Could she use it as a sitting room as well do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well she could have done but - I don't think she did much, she might have gone up there, but - not - not as a rule. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But she'd sit in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 If she wanted in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes, 'cos it was always lovely and warm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Would she sit with your mother and father in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not often. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You said that the girl who was the servant who you remember, I can't remember her name now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Eva Stiles. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You said that she was chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Like your parents?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Would your parents have hired her because she was chapel do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I - no, I don't think so, although I think it would have gone a long way in those days. But I don't think it - was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you think both families being chapel, how they went about hiring her would have had anything to do with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It might have done because they were both to do with the chapel, both the - men - well, and the - women. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You talked a bit about supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of things did you have for supper, did the children have their supper first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What would you have had for supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Oh I've got to think back there. Not a - not a big supper. Something to drink, generally milk, warm or cold, whichever - time. And not a - a lot to eat, probably biscuits or - bread and butter - for our supper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What would your parents have had later on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Oh - as far as I can remember - meat, you - you know, cut meat, and - probably some salad or - something from the garden like that. That was - generally theirs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about to drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well cold cocoa probably in the winter I know they used to like cocoa. And in the summer it would have been - lemonade. Chiefly, I don't think there was a lot more made you know. Made from the real lemons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did they make their own lemonade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Chiefly. Yes, well there wasn't anything hardly bottled you see in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You talked a bit about music at your grandmother's, at Christmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You said there was a piano and sometimes a fiddle, who would have played those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well - I don't - I don't think my father did much of that, it was an uncle, that was always there you see at the time, my mother's brother - that played the fiddle. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141  they have sort of get together}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141  at other times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well - it wouldn't be so big - as at Christmas, because they probably couldn't all get there, but - very often on a Sunday evening you see, go home from church or chapel, whichever the case - and you invited - friends in and - nearly always end
ed up with a - sing-song. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of songs did you sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well if it was Sunday it was chiefly hymns. And - oh I can't remember what was - going in those days. That's a little - that's a little bit of a problem. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you spend a lot of time at your grandparents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well we - we were always coming over to visit them, I don't say stay a long time, we stayed a few days at Christmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you stay at any other times, Easter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, we used to come over for the day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you like going to your grandparents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh always. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What was life like there, did they have two or three servants?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 There was always one servant there 'cos it was a - it's a huge house, if you've seen it, have you up - White House, it'
s a big one. And - somebody coming in to help as a rule. Like - in those days you had a washerwoman because there was no washing machines. See, anything like that, it all had to be done by hand. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You also said that your parents went visiting quite a lot, or went to visit farms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And you sometimes went with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What would you do, what would they do when you went visiting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, very often - the same as if they came to us you know, there'd be - social eve
nings in those days which generally meant a game of cards, whist or something of that, and - and - tennis, a lot of tennis in the summer. That was - and croquet. And - of course bowls. That was another - one that they played in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did a lot of people have tennis courts or things which you could play tennis on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well yes, we'd got a tennis court which could be turned into a croquet one and which could be turned into a bowling green, you see, it was made to - like for that - most of the farmers had a - tennis court you see. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Your parents were teachers at Sunday school were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were they anything else at chapel? Was your father a lay preacher at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well not exactly but he would take a - service if necessary, 
and they were both in the choir. But - you - you wouldn't call him a lay preacher, he didn't go out preaching. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was he a member of the Board of Chapel Guardians or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well he used to go to the meetings but I can't remember that one. No. No, I'm - I'm sorry, I can't remember that one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you think that they were very different from other members of the chapel, were they a slightly different class than most members?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 We - if - probably - but not a lot of difference. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have a bicycle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How old were you when you had that, do you remember at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well I learned - on an old one I can remember it was - what do you call it - not pumped up - tyres, hard tyres, and you couldn't free wheel. We
ll we was more often off than on. But I - I learnt and then I - my grandfather gave me a - cycle when I could conquer it you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you used to go cycling?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, you know, backwards and forwards to Woodstock chiefly. And of course we lived
 on cycles - about the village, 'cos that was - well it was the only way you got about, unless you walked. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you go much walking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 A fair amount. Used to go out for - especially - in the woods you know when the primroses were out, that was 
a usual thing and bluebells and - you know all that kind of thing. Yes. We had a really good time you know back in those days, although probably the children today would think it was awful. But - it - if - it was a real good time. You had to make it. I me
an they don't today do they so much. No. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I was talking about social classes you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In Hanborough would you say that all the working class people, all the poor, had the same standard of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 More or less, because - very often they - worked for a farmer. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were there some families which were known as rough and some as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Oh yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What would you think characterised a rough family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Don't know how to put that. Hm. Well they
 were rough in speech of course. And - manners and - that kind of thing you know. Rough altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141 cleanliness}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - sometimes you got - the bad ones. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And drink or anything like that?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, there was - people got -
 drunk about the village. Yes, there was a fair amount, I - it - it wasn't a bad village take it on the whole, but - were some.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were there bad villages in Oxfordshire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I don't think so, I - I don't remember ever - being told that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember any distinction between a craftsman, a man with a skill and an ordinary labourer, being made in speech or any other way?

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well you see we always had a - how would they call them? Blacksmith, I mean that'd be craft wouldn't it? But it was a
lways more or less - a rough man but - I don't say a bad man, but he was generally rough. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 But was he thought slightly superior to the labourers because he'd got a skill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Probably yes. Yes. Yes, I should - I should think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, they weren't too bad. No, not - what's the word for it - bigoted - you'd call it, oh no, they weren't - too bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well, yes, I should think she - did, more or less I think we always went under the name the middle class. You know, in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What do you think she was thinking of when she made herself middle class, your father's occupation or her parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I should think both. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you think it was possible at that time to move from one class to another very easily?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, because in those days if you were born a farm labourer you went on the land and that was wh
ere you stay. Chiefly. There wasn't a lot of - getting away from the farm. In fact it was reckoned a jolly good - life really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember anybody being described as a real lady or a real gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In Hanborough. Mm. No, I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about in Woodstock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well those days you - you - always thought of the - Duke and all his family - chiefly about here, and of course there were some - big house like at - Woodstock House but I can't remember the people living there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 So somebody was called a real lady or a real gentleman because they were nobility?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes, that's right. That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you remember seeing a policeman around where you lived as a child?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Occasionally, but you only - we'd got one at Hanborough I mean, one, you see, you saw him when he was out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were you ever sort of threatened with him, did your mother ever say if you're naughty I'll call the policeman or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. I don't remember that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How do you think he treated the people, particularly the poor in the village and how do you think they thought of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well - I should think the children of the poor ones - were probably a bit frightened of him. If you saw him uniform they'd run sometimes if they thought they'd done something wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When there was somebody in the district who the people sort of strongly disapproved of, was there any special way in which they showed it?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh I - I don't really know. What they disapproved of the bad ones you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Did you ever know for instance in Hanborough of anything called rough music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I - I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 People gathering outside somebody's house and banging dustbin lids and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No. I never saw any of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were you given any lessons by your parents or a tutor or a governess?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 We - now what about my brother, I went to - a little school in the village. A schoolteacher to start with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Let's see, it had to be five, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What time did you go to school in the morning and come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 About - yes nine 'til twelve and then in the afternoon two 'til four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You went to afternoon school straight away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of school was it, was it a private school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Well it - yes, it was just one teacher, and she took on this - the young ones you see, she didn't take on - much after I think about - seven or eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was it mixed, boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you get on at that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh all - all right I think. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you get to the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh walk, it wasn't very far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you go on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How long did it take you to walk there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I should think - ten minutes at the outmost.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You came home for your midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What did you feel about the lady who taught you, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well she was very nice person, more or less - ordinary, middle aged you know, but she was - she was very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did she emphasise certain things as being important in life that you remember? Like manners or ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, I don't think - not at that age. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did she punish the children in the school in any way at all if they were naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 We were kept in. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 She never used a cane?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were your parents very interested in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, they - kept up with that all the time, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did they come and visit the school or talk to the teacher or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well they knew her you see. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the other children in your school come from similar background to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Again - farmers. Chiefly, that's about all there was round Hanborough you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the farm labourers children go to the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 To this one, oh it was only a very little one, and - no, they didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you think this lady who taught you singled out some children for special attention?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No. She was very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, it wasn't big enough. Really for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Then you went on to another school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What was the next school you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oxford House school, went to Oxford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How old were you when you went there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - I should - think if I remember rightly about ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of school was that, was that a private school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes, yes, it was in those days, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was it a mixed school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 In the infants, I mean that was a - it was a proper school, there were some little boys, you know, the i
nfants, but as you got older there wasn't a - not any boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you get to school there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Train.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 From Woodstock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 From Hanborough. I'm talking - I was still at Hanborough when I went to that school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How long did it take you to get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
What, to Oxford? Well you had to - cycle about - oh mile and a half. And - oh it wasn't a very long journey. No. About twenty minutes I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You went on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, there were some more children in the village you see, we all went together but - they didn't all go to - my school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You had your midday meal at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 We took sandwiches. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you like that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes. I liked school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you like the teachers there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes, they were very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about teaching you certain things were important at that school, did they do that there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, you had to behave, you would - you know, you were taught - those kind of things. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did they teach you that manners were important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about ways of speaking, did they teach you elocution or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not a - not a lot, they spoke properly - to you and you were expected to - copy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about discipline and there and punishment, if you did something that the teacher thought was wrong?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh well you were kept in or given so many lines and - you know, that - read so much that you didn't like and - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What sort of things would they do to get punishment like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well one thing not doing your homework. Night, you see, you always had homework to take home, that wasn't done. And you had a punishment.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And your parents went on showing interest in what you were doing at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did they visit that school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes. At odd times you now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 They'd come and talk to the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were the children of the same social group as you do you think in that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Much about the same, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 There were a lot of country children, farmers daughters and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Do you think there that the teachers showed any favouritism or anything towards anybody, or single out children who they thought were specially bright or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, if you - if you couldn't get - on, you now, in a subject they seemed to - try to - help you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have groups or gangs or anything there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, you could really say friends, you were - there was a little clique of you as friends but - not - not a gang.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the girls who came in from the country tend to be together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes. On the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And then the ones who came from Oxford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh no, no, we mixed. Yes, yes. That's right. Mm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, I don't think so looking back on it, it was - no, I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You finished at that school, you didn't go to another school after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When did you leave school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh - I must have been about - fifteen I should think. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I want to ask you now about after you left school and up to about 1819 really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 While you were at school did you have any part time job or anything you could earn any money with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 At - while I was at school? No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What was your first job you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh it's a job isn't it, my first job - oh - yes, a glove factory. In the office - you see, in the glove factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I think my mother went to see the head first in those days they always did you see, and then you - followed on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What exactly did you do in the office in the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Book keeping. Answering the phone and - you know, all that kind of thing to start with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Whose glove factory was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It's out of existence ages.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Lays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. One out the back here, oh whatever was the name of them? No, it's gone completely. Oh I've got it, Samanac. Samanac glove factory.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How many people worked in the office with you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 One - two in one office and there was - three girls in the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 About - oh I should expect the usual, about nine 'til one, then two 'til five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you work on Sunday at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Or Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did we - I think we had to work Saturday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have a half day in the week at all in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Only the - Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have any holidays with pay or anything do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You had a week's holiday. And I think we had pay. I'm nearly certain we did. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Can you remember what you were paid a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I think I started at fifteen shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you think at the time that was a fair}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8783994\charrsid16543141  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It wasn't bad actually was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, it - you had - you could do a lot with that in those days you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you give any money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes, nine shillings to my mother and I had six shillings and I was a millionaire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Was your money you gave to your mother spent on anything special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, just - housekeeping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you get on with the people you worked with?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Very well, yes, we weren't too bad. Mm hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did your employer treat you, was he a reasonable man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It was a she. And - she was strict but she was - very fair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you feel about her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - I think - most people liked her. But we didn't like to cross her. So therefore you tried to do right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you like the work or did you not like it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh it - was all right, yes. The glove factory itself was interesting you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the job alter your attitude to school in any way, did you feel that you wished you'd stayed on at school or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, not in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 When did you leave that job? Did you work there until you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Oh - no because I worked - in - in - you know the shop I'm in now, well that belonged to - my grandfather and my uncle and I went to that after I - left the glove factory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What year would you have left the glove factory, have you got any idea, would it have been during the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Mm. I can't remember how many years I were there. That's the trouble, it's so long ago isn't it to remember the - date. 1918 we came here you see. What was - what was the date of the great war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 1914 that broke out, August?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, it was over - no, it - it's over 1918 wasn't it, so - I was working after 1918 you see, so it was all - the war itself was over.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Your father died of course in 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 And you were still at school then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. Well - I was about to leave you see, I was about fifteen then. Yes, I was, fifteen you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You stayed at Brothertons at the ironmongers until you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you think you'd have preferred another sort of job either than the glowing or in the ironmongers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No, I was quite happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have to serve any training or apprenticeship for either of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you think that between the - people used to say there was 
a great division between trained craftsmen and workers in work places in those days, do you remember anything about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well they had - bit better pay, certain, and - I think they always felt - a little a - above - the - the ordinary man, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did the craftsman have a trade union in the gloving?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 I don't remember it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Would you say that full time work changed your attitude to life in any way do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You moved in 1918 just after you left school to Woodstock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You continued to live at home though until you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you think starting full time work changed your relationships with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. Yes, no, I don't - no, I don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 What about towards your little brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, much about the same it went on. About - just about the same really. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you spend your Sunday any differently when you were at work?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, we - we went to - chapel still, at odd times see, an
d - well odd times - every Sunday evening and - in the afternoon as rule. Not so much the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you take an active interest in chapel life, did you teach at Sunday school or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well - no, not really but I used to play the organ, I 
- I was very keen on the organ and - I - had some lessons. And I used to play for services.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 That was in the Wesleyan in Oxford Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No, Olivet in those days, that's down further, down - at the top of the hill, do you remember, do you know it,
 it's a house now. Mm. And it wasn't the Wes - Wesleyan, but it was - however did they call it, it - it was very much the same as a Wes - Wesleyan, but - that's where we went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It wasn't a Primitive Methodist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Do you know another name? That doesn't seem to ring a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 United independent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Free Methodists?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 It was called Olivet chapel. Mm. No. NO, I don't know what it was called. There's - I know it was much about the same kind of service.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you take an interest in politics-?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Even though your father had been a Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
You told me something about how you spent your spare time earlier, when you were at school, did you continue to spend your spare time in the same way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 
Yes - much about the same I think, there wasn't a lot of difference - it was - it hadn't got to the age of - dances and all that kind of thing. You went to several - socials they used to call them in those days. Where you went - chiefly games. 
Wasn't a lot of dancing.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you go out in the evenings then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Sometimes, to the se socials or - across to my grandparents you see, they only lived just across the road to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you make new friends after you left school, boys or girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 How did you meet them do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Why in the socials, you got to know them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you ever bring friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh yes, she - you could do that. Not so much boys in those days you weren't allowed to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have any special friends at that time, boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well there was one or two I worked with you see, we used to meet at our - houses and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 You went to see one another in your houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Chiefly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you go anywhere else with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Oh go to Oxford and go to the pictures. See, make up a little - gathering and go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Well I could always take them home. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did they expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. More or less. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8477944 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Did you have to be in by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10944618 DH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1190607\charrsid16543141 Yes. Generally - they liked you in before ten.
\par }}